<p><a href="http://www.stevenwhitfield.info" target="_blank">Steven Whitfield</a>, a graphic designer from Blitz, created this version of the home page from which I developed the final product. The new home page includes an interactive menu and full screen artwork which is designed primarily to engage the user. The website makes use of, but is not dependant on, JavaScript. It also uses responsive design to provide an enjoyable experience on any internet-enabled device.</p>
